metadata.name: 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐟𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐠𝐲𝐚𝐫𝐮
metadata.description:
Grand opening day has arrived! I'm so excited, I hope everyone will see me work and be jealous of how beautiful I look in my uniform. It could really have some alterations, some sequins and something brighter maybe... Well, over time I convince our senpai to let us wear some bolder uniforms.

''Hello don't forget to visit our Maid Café and have a great day''

✧ All bidders will get a delicious dish as a reward

✧ The auction winner will receive a thank you stamp
